  <phrase title="option_explain.cid_mapping" version_id="1" version_string="0.0.1"><![CDATA[Defines the mapping of the returned JSON structure to the singular CID value. 

For example:
<pre>
{
    "data": {
        "cid": "1373921",
        "personal": {
            "email": "example@example.com",
            "full_name": "Max Mustermann"
         }
    }
} 
</pre>

If we wanted to access the cid, we would use the string: <strong>data.cid</strong>.]]></phrase>
